<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.8">
<l>maṉcuṟumā liruñcōlai niṉṟamaṇāḷaṉār</l>
<l>neñcaniṟai koṇṭupōyiṉār niṉaikiṉṟilar</l>
<l>veñcuṭarpōy viṭiyāmalev viṭampukkatō</l>
<l>nañcuṭalan tuyiṉṟālnamak kiṉinallatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My beloved, who stands in misty Māliruñcōlai,</l>
<l>Took away the whole of my heart; he does not think [anything of it].</l>
<l>Was the blazing sun, having set, caught somewhere without dawning?</l>
<l>If this baneful body would sleep, it would yet be a good thing for us!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
